      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like shine with no chips, scratches, or imperfections of any kind. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with leather that looks and smells brand new and all electronics functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a complete service history and not a single leak or rattle. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that presents exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
