      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS timing. This example is mechanically sound, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already performed and a cooling system refresh recently completed. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile shifts, sending power through a factory limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry remains sharp with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring the chassis handles with its signature neutrality. While displaying minor cosmetic patina typical of an honest driver, the drivetrain remains robust and free of parasitic leaks. A visceral, high-RPM machine ready for the canyons.",
